entityType.description:
Activities can be attached to multiple Centers not just Customer. The following is the EntityType code used for each Center attachment.
1 = Bank; 2 = Broker; 3 = Company; 4 = Customer; 5 = Employee; 8 = User; 9 = Vendor; 
The Rest Model be translated from the text into the code for the Business logic model

